#### SSH Authentication for Git #######

1. Import Public key into the github server(github account)
2. Create a file called config(without any extension) at .ssh folder in user directory of Windows.

Follow the below syntax

``````
#This validation is for DevOps-Practice-Key.
Host github.com
	HostName github.com
	User git
	IdentityFile ~/DevOps-Practice-Key.pem
	
#This is for another github account authentication.
Host github.com
	HostName github.com-anotheraccount
	User git
	IdentityFile ~/DevOps-Practice-Key.pem
	

~ -----> means home folder (/c/users/username) 

``````
